arChildNodes.szComment:
Heavy smoke obscures the charred surroundings. Donan’s eyes dart over the wreckage.
He’s frantically searching for his son, desperately trying to hold his emotions in check.
In his head he knows it’s too late, but in his heart he hasn’t given up hope yet.

BLOOD PETALS float down from the sky.
One lands in the palm of Donan’s hand. He grimaces at the sight of it, then squeezes the petal in his fist.

Movement off-screen catches Donan’s attention. Atop the ruins of a building, LILITH appears.
Donan is startled at her presence, but he finds the courage to speak.
Lilith smirks, then looks back over her shoulder.

From the heavy smoke behind Lilith, a MONSTROUS FORM emerges: the AMALGAM OF RAGE.
A DEMONIC FIGURE (which we later learn is ASTAROTH) sits on its back, wearing YORIN’S SHOULDERPAD.
His hands are clutched around the beast’s reins. 
The Amalgam plods forward until the smoke disappears, bringing Astaroth into full view. 
Donan stares up at the demon and what is left of his son. He is utterly shocked and broken.
Donan falls to his knees, hopeless, despairing.
ON LILITH as she watches the meeting from atop the ruins.

The smoke gathers around Lilith like a cloak and she disappears.
Donan continues staring at Astaroth, unable to move, at a loss for words. 
The Player marches past him toward the demon, ready to face off against Astaroth.
